---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="Our privacy policy will help you understand what information is collected and how it is used."
  title="Privacy policy Â· Digiwha Studios"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20 lg:px-8">
    <div class="sm:pb:20 flex flex-col gap-4 pb-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-base">Last update: November 8, 2024</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="mb-4">
        At Digiwha Studios, we are committed to safeguarding your privacy. This Privacy Policy
        outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        We collect limited information about your website usage through Google Analytics:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-4">
        <li>
          Usage Data: We collect anonymous data about how you use our website, including:
          <ul class="ml-6 mt-2 list-inside list-disc space-y-2">
            <li>Pages visited and time spent on each page</li>
            <li>Your approximate geographic location</li>
            <li>The type of device and browser you're using</li>
            <li>How you reached our website (search engines, links, etc.)</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">2. How We Use This Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-4">
        <li>
          To understand how visitors use our website and identify areas for improvement
        </li>
        <li>
          To analyze the effectiveness of our content and website features
        </li>
        <li>
          To generate anonymous, aggregate statistics about our website traffic
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">3. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We use Google Analytics, which places cookies on your device to help us analyze how users engage with our website. You can prevent the setting of cookies by adjusting your browser settings. Google Analytics data is processed in a way that does not personally identify individual users.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">4. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        You have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-4">
        <li>Opt-out of Google Analytics tracking by using Google's Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</li>
        <li>Delete or block cookies through your browser settings</li>
        <li>Request information about the data we collect</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">5. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at [your contact email].
      </p>

      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be posted on this page with the updated date at the top.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>